## 🧪 Mathematical Model

### 🔹 Boids Velocity Update

v_i = w_s S_i + w_a A_i + w_c C_i

Where:

* (S_i) → Separation vector
* (A_i) → Alignment vector
* (C_i) → Cohesion vector

---

### 🔹 Anti-Gravity Motion

p(t+1) = p(t) + v(t) + \epsilon

Where:

* (\epsilon) = small random drift force

